### ===========================================
### EVENTOS/CRONOGRAMA API - Pruebas
### ===========================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3010/api/v1
@adminToken = Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
@userToken = Bearer YOUR_USER_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### ===========================================
### RUTAS PÚBLICAS (Sin autenticación)
### ===========================================

### 1. Obtener todos los eventos
GET {{baseUrl}}/events

### 2. Obtener eventos con filtros
GET {{baseUrl}}/events?type=class&year=2025&month=8&limit=10

### 3. Obtener eventos de un mes específico (con recurrentes calculados)
GET {{baseUrl}}/events/month/2025/8

### 4. Obtener evento por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/events/66b12345678901234567890a

### ===========================================
### RUTAS ADMIN (Requieren autenticación + rol admin)
### ===========================================

### 5. Crear evento único
POST {{baseUrl}}/events
Authorization: {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Clase de Abdomen Intensivo",
  "description": "Entrenamiento enfocado en fortalecer los músculos abdominales",
  "startDate": "2025-08-20T17:00:00.000Z",
  "endDate": "2025-08-20T18:00:00.000Z",
  "type": "class",
  "category": "Abdomen",
  "color": "#48bb78",
  "location": "Estudio Principal",
  "maxParticipants": 15,
  "instructor": "Sarah",
  "price": 2500,
  "isRecurring": false
}

### 6. Crear evento recurrente (Lunes y Miércoles)
POST {{baseUrl}}/events
Authorization: {{adminToken}}
