### 9. Actualizar evento
PUT {{baseUrl}}/events/66b12345678901234567890a
Authorization: {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Clase de Abdomen Intensivo - ACTUALIZADA",
  "maxParticipants": 20,
  "price": 3000,
  "color": "#EF4444"
}

### 10. Eliminar evento (soft delete)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/events/66b12345678901234567890a
Authorization: {{adminToken}}

### 11. Obtener estadísticas de eventos (solo admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/events/admin/stats
Authorization: {{adminToken}}

