### 14. Crear evento con datos inválidos
POST {{baseUrl}}/events
Authorization: {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "",
  "startDate": "fecha-invalida",
  "type": "tipo-invalido"
}

### 15. Crear evento recurrente sin días especificados
POST {{baseUrl}}/events
Authorization: {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Evento Recurrente Inválido",
  "startDate": "2025-08-20T17:00:00.000Z",
  "type": "class",
  "isRecurring": true
}

### 16. Obtener eventos de mes inválido
GET {{baseUrl}}/events/month/2025/13

### 17. Obtener evento con ID inválido
GET {{baseUrl}}/events/id-invalido

